CREATE OR REPLACE EXTERNAL TABLE `ddme000426-gopr4nla6zo-furyid.STG.Sortia_Embargos_InOut` (
  user_from    STRING,
  amount       STRING,
  case_file    STRING,
  court        STRING,
  cover_sheet  STRING,
  debt_id      STRING
)
OPTIONS (
  format = 'GOOGLE_SHEETS',
  skip_leading_rows = 1,
  sheet_range = 'Resultado!A2:F',
  uris = ['https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1zyhXcYfi7epUOjEyzeHA-nTYTAZryh74LArP39HzPN4/edit#gid=GID_DA_ABA']
);

CREATE OR REPLACE TABLE `ddme000426-gopr4nla6zo-furyid.STG.Sortia_Embargos_InOut_FE` AS

SELECT DISTINCT *
FROM (

  SELECT
    A.user_from,
    A.amount,
    A.case_file,
    A.court,
    A.cover_sheet,
    A.debt_id,
    A.case_file   AS EXPEDIENTE,
    A.court       AS JUZGADO,
    A.cover_sheet AS CARATULA,
    B.DEBT_ID             AS DEBT_ID_DISP,
    B.DEBT_USER_ID,
    B.DEBT_SITE_ID,
    B.DEBT_CURRENCY_ID,
    B.DEBT_DEBT_TYPE_ID,
    B.DEBT_CREATED_AT,
    B.DEBT_TOTAL_AMOUNT,
    B.DEBT_PAID_AMOUNT,
    B.DEBT_STATUS,
    B.DEBT_DESCRIPTION
  FROM `ddme000426-gopr4nla6zo-furyid.STG.Sortia_Embargos_InOut` A
  LEFT JOIN `meli-bi-data.WHOWNER.BT_MP_DISB_DEBT` B
    ON A.debt_id = CAST(B.DEBT_ID AS STRING)
   AND B.DEBT_DEBT_TYPE_ID IN (77, 437, 442, 459)
   AND DATE(B.DEBT_CREATED_AT) >= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 20 DAY)

  UNION ALL

  SELECT
    NULL AS user_from,
    NULL AS amount,
    NULL AS case_file,
    NULL AS court,
    NULL AS cover_sheet,
    NULL AS debt_id,
    'NA' AS EXPEDIENTE,
    'NA' AS JUZGADO,
    'NA' AS CARATULA,
    B.DEBT_ID             AS DEBT_ID_DISP,
    B.DEBT_USER_ID,
    B.DEBT_SITE_ID,
    B.DEBT_CURRENCY_ID,
    B.DEBT_DEBT_TYPE_ID,
    B.DEBT_CREATED_AT,
    B.DEBT_TOTAL_AMOUNT,
    B.DEBT_PAID_AMOUNT,
    B.DEBT_STATUS,
    B.DEBT_DESCRIPTION
  FROM `meli-bi-data.WHOWNER.BT_MP_DISB_DEBT` B
  WHERE B.DEBT_DEBT_TYPE_ID IN (77, 437, 442, 459)
    AND DATE(B.DEBT_CREATED_AT) >= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 20 DAY)

);
